item.title: It's the Osprey Delight demo site.
item.description: And here’s my repo! Osprey Delight is a sugar-free version of the awesome Osprey theme by Toma Nistor for Hugo. It tastes a bit different than the original (hence the “light” in the name) but also adds some new functionality – hopefully to your delight. Have fun using it!
